query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('electronics',
'magento',
'mathoverflow',
'pt',
'tex')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('array',
'beamer',
'bibliographies',
'graphics',
'json',
'laravel',
'magento2.3',
'math-mode',
'power-supply',
'product',
'python-3.x',
'r',
'sql-server',
'table-of-contents')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
